{"title":"新会小景","authors":["韩北屏","郁风"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新会小景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩北屏诗  郁风画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风云雷雨之神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传说龙潭深不见底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住有一位风云雷雨之神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"久旱、久阴，人们前往叩拜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望他及时雨来及时晴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往日的传说自然荒诞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天圭峰山上果然有“神灵”："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人造天湖汪洋一片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖水奔腾直泻龙潭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水电站的“法力无边”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发电房里制造出雷雨风云。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}